臨床鏡檢學（含實驗）                     CLINICAL MICROSCOPY INCLUDING LAB.


  	臨床鏡檢課程，旨在教學生瞭解門診常規檢查的基本原理及操作技巧。課程內容包括體液，胃液及十二指腸液檢驗﹑懷孕試驗﹑精液檢查等。涵蓋了臨床生化及臨床細菌學基本的概論。Clinical microscopy introduces the basic principles and skills of the routine examinations in out-patient department. It includes all the examinations of urine, feces, sputum, semen, body fluid, cerebrospinal fluid, gastric juice and bile analysis, pregnancy test, and synopsis of clinical biochemistry and microscopy. (Young, Kung-Chia)

課程教育目標 

A 養成有愛心能力優秀有理想之醫檢人才 Train benevolent and excellent medical laboratory scientist. 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

E 醫學檢驗之基本能力

H 專業素養


